==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coloration
<hw>Col`or*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or art
of coloring; the state of being colored.</def>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The females . . . resemble each other in their general type of
<qex>coloration</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Darwin.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Colorature</ent>⟦br⟧
